  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Cases: Man from couples with RPL (more than 2 miscarriages) RPL classical etiological
             exploration negative (unexplained RPL) Healthy voluntaries

          -  Control: Man from couples who have a child after a natural pregnancy obtained in the
             year following child desire.

        Healthy voluntaries

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Cases: Etiological exploration of RPL positive Man with chromosomal anomaly

          -  Cases and controls:

        Ongoing pathology Chemotherapy or radiotherapy history Hyperthermia (fever) in the last
        three months Pregnancy obtained by assisted reproduction (Inseminations, in vitro
        fertilization) Women &gt; 38 year old
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
